vering the AI Readiness Assessment and a 90-day implementation roadmap; a Growth engagement at $2,497 covering full Tier 1 deployment; and an Enterprise engagement with custom pricing for multi-system implementations. For Retail businesses in Manama, Bahrain, the right starting point depends on your current data infrastructure and the complexity of your customer communication workflow. See the full pricing breakdown at /resources/ai-consulting-cost-qatar."},{"q":"Is AI implementation compliant with data protection laws in Manama, Bahrain?","a":"Yes — all AI Navigator engagements include a data governance review appropriate to your jurisdiction. Data protection requirements vary across GCC countries, and the correct framework is identified and applied before any AI system handling personal data is deployed."}]}]]}]
